dream about a ghostly figured killer i often dreamt that i was been chased by a black hooded killer almost like a ghost with barely seen faced it killed the people i don't know and have met before it really scared me every time i woke up with that dream it felt almost real it's like i've been running all night it's like a harry potter like dream it really bothers me during the day when i woke up with that dream according to dreamcrowd in general ghosts symbolizes aspects of yourself that you fear this may involve a painful memory guilt or some repressed thoughts you may be afraid of death and dying alternatively ghosts are representative of something that is no longer obtainable or within reach it indicates a feeling of disconnection from life and society this dream may be a calling for you to move on and abandon your outdated modes of thinking and behavior to dream that you reach out to touch a ghost but it disappears indicates that you are taking steps to acknowledging some painful or repressed thoughts even though you are not ready to fully confront them to see the ghost of a living relative or friend in your dream signifies that you are in danger of malice acts by that person to see the ghost of a dead friend relative in your dream suggests guilt and regrets concerning the past relationships with that particular person to see a killer in your dream suggests that an essential aspect of your emotions have been cut off you feel that you are losing your identity and your individuality alternatively this dream may represent purification and the healing process you are standing up for yourself and putting a dramatic end to something try posting your dream on dreamcrowd for a free interpretation Sigmund Freud Yoga Sutras of Patanjali Dead Like Me Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban Knots Landing Ghost The Amber Spyglass Baptism Scenes from a Memory Characters of The Sandman Scientology beliefs and practices Dream Similarities between the Bible and the Qur'an Out-o